snippet.title: Battle Wrath gameplay (PC Game, 1997)
snippet.description:
Gameplay for Battle Wrath, Dos PC game produced by Cerebral Gaming Systems in 1997 - http://www.squakenet.com/download/battle-wrath/6420/
Trying out a few fighters in this old-school one-on-one beat 'em up.
Played through Dosbox emulation platform.
Recorded with original sound.
